  "summary" : "The Unified Layer is proposed as a central, interoperable platform by NPCI to facilitate standardized communication and information sharing between government agencies and participant banks. This platform aims to streamline the delivery of government benefits and subsidies by providing standardized APIs for data upload, lookup, update, and transaction initiation, reducing the need for multiple bilateral integrations and enhancing transparency and auditability in the CBDC ecosystem.",
